Physics Informed Neural Network

Forward Problem: 1D Heat Equation and Viscous Burgers Equation

Structure:
pinn/
├── README
├── src/
│   ├── model.py           # PINN class (nn.Module)
│   ├── physics.py         # PDE residual, BC/IC functions
│   ├── train.py           # training loop, Adam + L-BFGS
│   ├── sampling.py        # collocation point generation
│   ├── eval.py            # error metrics
│   ├── plot.py            # plotting helpers
│   └── run_experiments.py # runs all 8 experiment configurations
├── experiments/
│   └── 1d_heat.py         # standalone heat equation script
├── logs/                  # Python run timing logs and eval results
│   ├── evals.csv
│   ├── experiment_manifest.json
│   └── perf_<name>_<time>.csv
├── plots/                 # generated figures
├── cpp/                   # C++ port (LibTorch)
│   ├── include/           # header files
│   │   ├── model.hpp
│   │   ├── physics.hpp
│   │   ├── train.hpp
│   │   ├── sampling.hpp
│   │   └── eval.hpp
│   ├── src/               # implementation files
│   │   ├── model.cpp
│   │   ├── physics.cpp
│   │   ├── train.cpp
│   │   ├── sampling.cpp
│   │   ├── eval.cpp
│   │   ├── eval_main.cpp
│   │   └── run_experiments.cpp
│   ├── third_party/
│   │   └── hermite_nodes_50.hpp
│   ├── build/
│   │   ├── bin/           # compiled executables
│   │   └── obj/           # object files
│   └── make_experiments   # primary makefile
├── c_logs/                # C++ run timing logs and eval results
│   ├── evals.csv
│   ├── experiment_manifest.json
│   └── perf_<name>_<time>.csv
└── c_runs/                # saved C++ model checkpoints (.pt)

---

Python Training

  cd /PINN
  python src/run_experiments.py

Output: model checkpoints in runs/, timing logs in logs/, eval results in logs/evals.csv

---

C++ Training (LibTorch)

Requirements: GCC 12.3.0, CMake 3.25.2, LibTorch

  module load gcc/12.3.0
  module load cmake/3.25.2

Navigate to the cpp directory:

  cd /PINN/cpp

Build:

  make -f make_experiments LIBTORCH=/fs/scratch/PAS2137/libtorch

Run all 8 experiments:

  build/bin/pinn_experiments

Output: model checkpoints in c_runs/, timing logs in c_logs/, eval results in c_logs/evals.csv
